features: DERMATOLIGISIT TESTED TO CALM & SOOTHE: This gentle-yet-effective, facial toner cleanses and removes residual oils, dirt and makeup for healthy-looking skin that’s ready for the next step in your skin care.
DESIGNED FOR SENSITIVE SKIN to balance and reduce the appearance of redness. This alcohol-free toner gently cleanses without stripping your skin.
FORMULATED WITH CUCUMBER EXTRACT, Witch Hazel and Aloe Vera, this alcohol-free cocktail of pH balancing powerhouses, helps tone, hydrate and nourish without stripping or drying out sensitive skin.
HOW TO USE: After cleansing, saturate a cotton pad with toner and apply all over face, avoiding the eye area. No need to rinse, simply follow up with treatment and moisturizer.

OVER 95% NATURAL INGREDIENTS of consciously created skincare made just for you. Formulated without Parabens, SLS and Silicones! Cruelty-Free & Leaping bunny certified which means no testing on animals leaving you confident in your trusted beauty brand.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Our Mission Yes To helps you make better skincare choices by providing clean and efficacious natural beauty solutions. Known for our fruit and veggie-based products that feature at least 95% natural ingredients (before water), our formulations are Leaping Bunny Certified, dermatologist tested and free of over 2,000 questionable ingredients, including those banned by the EU and Canada. Yes To is proud to offer intuitive skincare that’s inspired by nature and designed to deliver the quality you crave. Yes To Cucumbers Daily Gentle Toner For Sensitive Skin Set the tone with cucumbers to help keep sensitive skin feeling balanced and beautiful. This refreshing, alcohol-free toner gently cleanses, removing residual oils, dirt and makeup without stripping the skin. Formula is enriched with cucumber extract, witch hazel and aloe vera to help balance, tone, hydrate, nourish and calm sensitive skin. For use morning and night, after cleansing but before moisturizing. Ideal for sensitive skin. 97% natural ingredients. Formulated without Parabens, SLS and Silicones. Dermatologist tested. Non-comedogenic. Leaping Bunny Certified. Vegan.

Other Items to Consider from Yes To Cucumbers Calming Facial Wipes Yes To Cucumbers Hypoallergenic Facial Wipes gently remove dirt, sweat and makeup (eye makeup too!) without the need to rinse. Whether you’re out and about, going for a run, or having a late night, these wipes make it a snap to refresh on-the-go. Packed with green superfoods these all-natural wipes naturally refresh and rejuvenate all-in-one. Stay gorgeous, and go from zero to clean in seconds! Cucumbers Cooling Jelly Mask Yes to jellin’ out with cucumbers to quench, soften and help calm skin. Formulated with cucumber extract, this lightweight, bouncy gel mask packs a hydrating punch that leaves skin feeling cool, soothed and refreshed. The transparent green formula dries down quickly, leaving skin feeling soothed in just 10 minutes! Cucumbers Daily Gentle Moisturizer When it comes to soothing, we’ve got you covered. Treat your face to some “me-time” and soothe your troubles away with this skin-soothing moisturizer that calms your delicate skin and enhances your complexion’s natural glow with a gentle burst of hydration. Lovingly formulated for sensitive skin, this light and creamy daily facial lotion delights your skin with an extra dose of proteins and nutrients. Formulated with Cucumber Extract, Aloe, and Sweet Almond Oil, this moisturizer gently soothes, smooths and hydrates your skin almost instantly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It cleans my skin really well, it feels fresh, it is not harsh. I buy this product on a regular basis and I like it a lot.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lasts A Long Time.
reviews.reviewText: Since the instructions on the back of this container of toner say all that’s needed is two presses on a cotton pad once daily, it lasts a while. I like that this toner contains the ingredient Hyaluronate, which after two months of continuous use should lessen the slight increase of pimple breakouts my normal type skin is having, due to the humidity fluctuations of the weather. The grapefruit scent is fresh, crisp and not sweet or strong.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a nice and very gentle toner for sensitive skin. The bottle is so easy to use, just push your cotton ball on top. It removes all dirt off my face, leaving it clean and fresh. It is a bargain at under $5.00. This will tighten your pores with daily use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for my pre-teen!
reviews.reviewText: My stepdaughter loves the scent and it leaves her skin full and clean and refreshed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Really tightens pores and refreshes the skin. Pleasant scent too

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My skin seems to really love skincare that has some fruit aspect to it. I bought this, it is the only change in my routine, diet, lifestyle. I started getting a white pimple every few days or so. I mean actual pimples not those you can just sorta scratch off with a napkin.Haven't really had this problem before, not in recent memory.30s, skin is NOT sensitive, healthy moisture barrier, not dry or overly oily, I no longer struggle with acne.A "your results may vary" kind of product. The smell and experience of applying the product is pleasant enough. I do not see any real benefits that I don't feel a similar product couldn't replicate.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Great moisturizing toner, non itching. Face feels soft, love the easy pump.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on October 2, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a great product, skin feels really clean afterwards, with no stickiness or residue left behind. My skin also feels brighter and fresher with regular use. No need to spend a fortune on acid exfoliators when this does the job so well.
